text: Azuqueca de Henares is a village in the west of the province of Guadalajara (Castile-La Mancha), in Spain The village has a population of 35,397, in the 2013 census. 2013 census: retrieved 12 August 2015 == References == Category:Municipalities in Castile-La Mancha Category:Province of Guadalajara
title: Azuqueca de Henares
